  "description": "当用户使用没有通过苹果授权的Lightning线缆连接运行iOS 7的设备时，系统会发出警告。经告终写到“该线缆或外设没有通过苹果审核，可能不会与iPhone可靠的工作。”<b>虽然有警告信息，不过这些非授权的线缆还 是可以正常使用的。iOS 7既然能检测到这些非授权线缆，这意味着苹果就可以遮蔽他们，不过苹果并没有选择这么做。</b><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2d2fe0ec/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240833.htm&amp;t=iOS+7%E7%BB%86%E8%8A%82%E6%94%B9%E5%8F%98%EF%BC%9A%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E9%9D%9E%E6%8E%88%E6%9D%83%E7%9A%84Lightning%E7%BA%BF%E7%BC%86%E4%BC%9A%E5%8F%91%E5%87%BA%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240833.htm&amp;t=iOS+7%E7%BB%86%E8%8A%82%E6%94%B9%E5%8F%98%EF%BC%9A%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E9%9D%9E%E6%8E%88%E6%9D%83%E7%9A%84Lightning%E7%BA%BF%E7%BC%86%E4%BC%9A%E5%8F%91%E5%87%BA%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240833.htm&amp;t=iOS+7%E7%BB%86%E8%8A%82%E6%94%B9%E5%8F%98%EF%BC%9A%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E9%9D%9E%E6%8E%88%E6%9D%83%E7%9A%84Lightning%E7%BA%BF%E7%BC%86%E4%BC%9A%E5%8F%91%E5%87%BA%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240833.htm&amp;t=iOS+7%E7%BB%86%E8%8A%82%E6%94%B9%E5%8F%98%EF%BC%9A%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E9%9D%9E%E6%8E%88%E6%9D%83%E7%9A%84Lightning%E7%BA%BF%E7%BC%86%E4%BC%9A%E5%8F%91%E5%87%BA%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.co